    "description": "<p>The Dempsey Project is a welcoming space to browse, dine, and unwind—from morning through evening.<br>\n<br>\nWhether you settle into our communal dining area or relax in a wicker chair on the veranda, you’ll find yourself immersed in the timeless charm of Dempsey Hill. Once home to towering nutmeg plantations, this peaceful enclave is now the setting for our thoughtfully curated oasis.<br>\n<br>\nOur menu is as diverse as our guests—ranging from wholesome to indulgently satisfying, with options for vegan, vegetarian, and gluten-free diets. Whatever your taste, we’re sure you’ll find a reason to return.</p>",
